	dwg: add unsorted MATERIAL fields
	needs CFLAGS="-DDEBUG_MATERIAL"

	so far the first two text fields: name, desc are known, the rest unknown.

2018-05-31  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	dxf: fix LTYPE table

