	[v] Fix bug: Collapse individual tuple-item assignments.
	* testsuite/xmlsuite/check.py <top-level>:
	  Don't assign to ‘result[0]’ and ‘result[1]’ separately;
	  instead, assign a literal 2-tuple to ‘result’, once.

